class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買生果個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n探病咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 借啲二話食飯加送買啲名貴飯送啦咩燒鵝果啲 老人家好受呢啲架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係水果係最好架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真 水果似去醫院探病"},{"pid":"af6894733167691ffd89b25c6f9e17c29aecd3cd","tid":6872,"uid":20168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"買支紅酒"},{"pid":"ed6cd6930681dddf2518a56ed5d5d52c093dfc9e","tid":6872,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"買啲靚嘢<br />\n貴價朱古力、燕窩、花膠之類<br />\n最緊要取悅未來奶奶<br />\n未來老爺唔駛買嘢俾佢<br />\n當然你都可以問下你男友意見"},{"pid":"07c4776142c3b621aeeeaf0d838a95abdf74f3f0","tid":6872,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T16:58:17.000Z","msg":"買菊花"},{"pid":"dd65776e30f69d6615b478a62149e355c29445c5","tid":6872,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:00:41.000Z","msg":"屌你，水果可以買切好果d果盤架嘛，唔市真係成籃水果拎去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地如果ok刺身既咪買d貴些少果d，嫌唔夠加多枝白酒，fit喇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0a36bf0fdce0f8a3ff0539ffb46a762c01d9f2","tid":6872,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"認真答<br />\n未食飯前就扮野睇下有咩幫手<br />\n幫手鋪下拎下飯碗咁囉<br />\n飯後扮野話幫手洗碗 通常都會叫你唔洗 <br />\n但有扮點都好過無<br />\n如果Auntie uncle 夾餸俾你講唔該<br />\n禮貌 扮乖 一入門口要大聲叫auntie uncle <br />\n搵topic傾 同你男朋友打聽下中意乜 通常咪又係傾下女人野  份人要talkative 啲<br />\n送禮我覺得未必 可以既睇下送乜 可能生果 海味個啲囉 不過唔識揀分分鐘自己柒左<br />\n參考來源：我老母"},{"pid":"b404e97f8aabe78804589eefdf931a0c8896a264","tid":6872,"uid":12967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:58:31.000Z","msg":"之前唔知邊到睇過送下花膠花旗"},{"pid":"ecbe8c35583ba21617eae3fc65123fea6981491b","tid":6872,"uid":12967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前唔知邊到睇過送下花膠花旗参之類煲湯野auntie至鐘意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n手殘send左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bdb317de36627fa0d1e756d9c818070c16f9e6","tid":6872,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:39:48.000Z","msg":"第一次見咩都冇買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能仲係學生 男朋友媽媽都冇咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗諗真係輕鬆好多<br />\n但上次佢媽媽生日叫埋我去食飯 心諗點都要買啲野掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行左兩三個鐘先求其買左啲野 仲因爲遲左搞到男朋友比人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}